    dc:date "2011" ;
    dc:title "Two new species of the genus Geocharis Ehlers, 1883 and new data on Anillina species from Portugal (Coleoptera: Carabidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207164>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207165>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207166>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207167>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207162> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207164>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. SEM photographs of structural features of Geocharis antheroi n. sp., (a), head (latero – dorsal view); (b), head (ventral view); (c), pronotum (dorsal view); (d), elytra (dorsal view); (e), right elytron (latero-dorsal view); (f), anterior half of elytra (dorsal view); (g), thorax and abdomen (male, ventral view); (h), thorax and abdomen (female, ventral view)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/207164/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207165>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Geocharis barcorabelo n. sp. aedeagus, (a), median lobe and left paramere in lateral view; (b), apex of median lobe in dorsal view. Geocharis antheroi n. sp. aedeagus, (c), median lobe and left paramere in lateral view; (d), apex of median lobe in dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/207165/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207166>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. SEM photographs of female genitalia in ventral view: (a) Geocharis barcorabelo n. sp.; (b) Geocharis antheroi n. sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/207166/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207167>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Geographical distribution in Portugal (U. T. M. 10 x 10 km coordinates) of G. barcorabelo n. sp. (B), G. a n t h e ro i n. sp. (A), G. olisipensis (O), G. quartaui (Q), and H. lusitanicus (L) (red colour capitals)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/207167/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.207162>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. The habitat of G. a n t h e ro i n. sp. in Carção (Vimioso region)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/207162/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

